race.comment: HUSTLE (7) resumes and has placed 2/2 fresh, including at Moonee Valley on debut. Has jumped out well at Flemington and draws an inside gate with Meech booked. Suited and looks ready to go. WHITSON (14) impressed coming from the back at Bendigo beaten 0.7L. Deserves another win and gets his chance. HUGHIE (3) brings two near misses and was a short-priced favourite at St Arnaud last time. Has the speed to manage the awkward and will go close with average luck. ZAMORA (12)  registered a strong win at Gunbower two runs ago but was a bit plainer at Horsham following (vet cleared). Peaks for this and can't be ruled out.
